Presstoff (also Prestoff or Pressstoff) is the German-language term for a type of ersatz or artificial leather used during the first half of the 20th century. Made of specially layered and treated paper pulp, Presstoff was durable and easily adapted to be used in place of leather. In minecraft this is made by throwing paper into sewage water - it's true!
